title: The Bled Discography (2001-2010)
description:
The Bled - Discography (2001-2010)

MP3 @ 128-256 Kbps,

(2001) His First Crush
(2002) The Bled
(2003) Pass The Flask
(2005) Found In The Flood
(2007) Pass The Flask (Reissue Bonus Tracks)
(2007) Silent Treatment
(2010) Heat Fetish

Bonus Songs
The Bled/Alexisonfire Split

**His First Crush and The Bled are taken off the reissue of Pass The Flask, the reissue is just the bonus tracks the rset are on (2003) Pass The Flask. 
Also the versions of Ambulance Romance, and Catholic Schoolgirl Blues were ripped form the internet. 

All of the albums I found in zip links on Russian forums so I thought I'd compile a full discography of everything listed on their wiki except
The Bled / From Autumn to Ashes split because as far as I can tell the exact copies of the songs "My Assassin" and "She Calls Home" were the ones put on
"Found In The Flood"

This is also my first attempt at uploading a torrent, so feedback would be great.
